Summary:        Preload library to back text, data, malloc() or shared memory with hugepages
Name:           libhugetlbfs
Version:        2.22
Release:        1%{?dist}
License:        LGPL-2.1
URL:            https://github.com/libhugetlbfs/libhugetlbfs
